					<span class="stat-value" data-mirror="block-height">—</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-label">Epoke:</span>
					<span class="stat-value" data-mirror="epoch">—</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-label">Blokke til næste epoke:</span>
